{
  "stem": "1473.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] I understand that, when she was a teenager and after my, my-- after all, she was born in '97.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her father died in '14.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sent her to a commercial school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she became a bookkeeper.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, she kept the books for the store for a number of years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was a bookkeeper.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she was talented.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother sang well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother could look in a-- in a magazine-- she could look at a dress and buy, very cheaply, a little remnant.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then she would take, I remember, newspaper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she would cut a pattern and make us all dresses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sure, she made all my dresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She made some of her sister's dresses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She made-- the only times I played with dolls, as a matter of fact, is when my mother made dresses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Otherwise, I had very little interest in dolls except when they didn't belong to me but to my cousin.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then I wanted those dolls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the-- and she taught me how to knit and sew when I was very little.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I loved that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I enjoyed that very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she was a sensitive-- a very sensitive woman, very committed to Zionism, very, very committed to Palestine and to the thought of leaving all this behind.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And someday-- her dream was someday, Eretz Yisrael.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they sent me-- she sent me to a Hebrew school, which was twice a week after school and on Sunday mornings.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they tell me that I became quite proficient in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It must have been true because when we reached Belgium, my mother and my aunt-- the day after we arrived-- took me to school and to the Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
